# CODEOWNERS for cyberos
#
# This file pins specific paths to required reviewer teams. Combined with
# branch-protection rules requiring "review from code owners", a PR
# touching a pinned path cannot merge without that team's approval.
#
# Legal-team gating (FR-CHAT-001 §1 #5 — README §2):
#   - services/chat/PINNED_COMMIT          immutable license-posture anchor
#   - services/chat/patches/**             cherry-picks from upstream
#   - services/chat/CHANGELOG.cyberos.md   reviewed alongside patches
#   - services/email/docker/stalwart.toml  Stalwart server config (security-critical)
#   - services/email/migrations/**         message metadata + DKIM keystore schemas
#
# Security-team gating:
#   - services/auth/**                     all AUTH module changes
#   - services/email/src/dkim/**           DKIM keystore Rust code
#   - .github/workflows/**                 CI workflow definitions
#
# Default owner: @cyberos/engineering

* @cyberos/engineering

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CHAT service — fork-licensing posture
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
services/chat/PINNED_COMMIT                @cyberos/legal-team @cyberos/engineering
services/chat/CYBEROS_PATCH_VERSION        @cyberos/legal-team @cyberos/engineering
services/chat/patches/**                   @cyberos/legal-team @cyberos/engineering
services/chat/CHANGELOG.cyberos.md         @cyberos/legal-team @cyberos/engineering

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# EMAIL service — Stalwart deployment + DKIM keystore
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
services/email/docker/stalwart.toml        @cyberos/security-team @cyberos/engineering
services/email/migrations/**               @cyberos/security-team @cyberos/engineering
services/email/src/dkim/**                 @cyberos/security-team @cyberos/engineering

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AUTH service — RBAC + RLS + JWT (security-critical)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
services/auth/**                           @cyberos/security-team @cyberos/engineering

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CI workflows
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.github/workflows/**                       @cyberos/devops-team @cyberos/engineering
.github/CODEOWNERS                         @cyberos/legal-team @cyberos/security-team
